ess10 = read.csv("ESS10.csv")
ess10.dematt = ess10 %>% select(
  fairelc, 
  dfprtal,
  medcrgv,
  rghmgpr,
  cttresa,
  votedir,
  gptpelc,
  viepol,
  wpestop,
  keydec,
  gvctzpv,
  grdfinc)
ess10.dematt[ess10.dematt > 10] = NA
boxplot(ess10.dematt, horizontal = T)

source("customplots.r")
plot_corheat(ess10.dematt, lowerhalf = TRUE)

KMO(cor(ess10.dematt, use = "pairwise.complete.obs"))

  ess10.dematt,
  weight = ess10$anweight,
  nfactors = 3,
  fm = "minres",
  scores = "tenBerge")

# Lookup table: Majority ancestries per country
maj = c(
# AT = 11010,
  BG = 14030,
  CH = 11100,
  CZ = 15020,
# DE = 11070,
  EE = 15030,
# ES = 13070,
  FI = 12020,

  GR = 13030,
  HR = 14040,
  HU = 15040,
  IS = 12030,
  IT = 13040,
  LT = 15060,
  ME = 14080,
  MK = 14060,
  NL = 11040,
  NO = 12040,
# PL = 15090,
  PT = 13060,
# RS = 14110,
# SE = 12060,
  SI = 14120,
  SK = 15130)
ds =
  as.data.frame(fact$scores) %>%
  data.frame(ess10.dematt) %>%
  mutate(lib = MR1) %>%
  mutate(abs = MR2) %>%
  mutate(soc = MR3) %>%
  mutate(libprio = lib - abs)

ds$dscrgrp = ess10$dscrgrp
ds$dscrgrp[ds$dscrgrp > 2] = NA
ds$dscrgrp[ds$dscrgrp == 2] = 0
ds$dscrgrp = as.logical(ds$dscrgrp)

ds$cntry = as.factor(ess10$cntry)

ds$ethmin = ess10$anctry1 != maj[ess10$cntry]

ds$polintr = ess10$polintr
ds$polintr[ds$polintr > 4] = NA
ds$polintr = 5 - ds$polintr

ds$lrscale = ess10$lrscale
ds$lrscale[ds$lrscale > 10] = NA

ds$gndr = ess10$gndr
ds$gndr[ds$gndr > 2] = NA
ds$gndr = as.factor(ds$gndr)

ds$age = ess10$agea
ds$age[ds$age > 150] = NA
boxplot(ds %>% select(lib, abs, soc, libprio))

plot_corheat(ds, lowerhalf = TRUE)

table(ds$dscrgrp)
## 
## FALSE  TRUE 
## 30423  2443
table(ds$ethmin)
## 
## FALSE  TRUE 
## 28582  4769
mod_lib = lmer(
  lib ~ ethmin + lrscale + polintr + gndr + age + (1 | cntry),
  data = ds, weight = ess10$anweight)
